headline: People Helping People Receives $75,000 Grant from KeyBank to Support Employment Opportunities for Underserved Women
summary: SALT LAKE CITY /3BL/- KeyBank has awarded a $75,000 grant to People Helping People in Salt Lake City, a nonprofit providing employment training and resources to low-income women and single mothers...
